---
<section class="cta" id="contact">
  <div class="wrap cta-grid">
    <div class="side">
      <div class="num">§ 03 · Contact</div>
      <h2 class="display">Send us<br />the brief.</h2>
      <p>This form goes directly to the engineering team. One engineer reads it. One engineer replies — within one business day.</p>
      <p style="color:#8A8378;font-size:13.5px;font-family:var(--mono);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase">
        Free pilot · NDA-friendly · No mailing list
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="form">
      <div class="form-head">
        <div class="t">§ 03.1 · Contact form</div>
        <div class="r"><span class="dot"></span>Team available</div>
      </div>
      <form>
        <div class="fg row2">
          <div><label>Name</label><input type="text" placeholder="Your name" required /></div>
          <div><label>Role</label><input type="text" placeholder="Senior piping engineer" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fg row2">
          <div><label>Company</label><input type="text" placeholder="Design institute / EPC" required /></div>
          <div><label>Corporate email</label><input type="email" placeholder="name@company.com" required /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fg">
          <label>What you'd like us to do</label>
          <textarea placeholder="Scope, approximate segment count, deadline, any constraint notes…"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-note">
          <b>Don't attach files here.</b> Reply to our email with PCF / Isogen export + tracing brief — no conversions, no cloud upload. Write to <code>engineering@traceopt.com</code>.
        </div>
        <div class="form-submit">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg">Send brief →</button>
          <div class="legal">By submitting you agree to the <a href="#" style="color:#A39E92;text-decoration:underline">privacy policy</a>.</div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
